Controversial director Chima Okoroji has blamed the parents of actor Yul Edochie for the second wife he took. He said getting a son from his second wife Judy Austin was all the fault of the actor’s parents Okoroji a-look-alike of music superstar Davido, said: “I am not surprised about what has happened between Yul and Judy Austin. We need to look at the root cause of Yul’s action before we apportion blame.   I don’t mind being Yul Edochie’s third wife – Amanda…     ‘Most ladies condemning polygamy date married…     I’ve never seen a faithful actor, says Iyabo Ojo   “Yul at a tender age when most young men were exhibiting their prowess and getting adventurous got a girl pregnant and based on tradition was forced to marry at that very young age without checking the effect of that action on his youthful age. “Our parents should take precaution about this kind of situation. They should allow their children to get mature enough to decide on what they want.”